Keep the amount of vegetation to a bare minimum in this zone. Your 1st zone should be at least 30 feet (9.14 m) around your house. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/aa/Prevent-Arson-in-Your-Community-Step-17Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Prevent-Arson-in-Your-Community-Step-17Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/aa/Prevent-Arson-in-Your-Community-Step-17Bullet4.jpg/v4-760px-Prevent-Arson-in-Your-Community-Step-17Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

You can plant alternative trees and shrubs. Some good options for this zone and beyond include buckthorn, lilac, maple and birch. Ensure all shrubs and trees are maintained and far enough away from structures. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c5/Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c5/Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet1.jpg/v4-760px-Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

This area should start at the end of your 1st buffer zone and extend to at least 100 feet (30.5 meters). Your zone might extend out further if you live on a hill. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/88/Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/88/Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet2.jpg/v4-760px-Prepare-for-a-Forest-Fire-Step-6Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
